Effective Date:
1.11.2024
Netogami Co. Ltd. ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting
          the privacy of users ("you" or "your") of the CozyBrushery app. This
          Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard
          your information when you use our app.
1. Information We Collect
Email Address:
When you sign up for CozyBrushery,
            we collect your email address. This is the only personal information
            we collect.
Device Token:
When you first start the App, we
            generate a random token to identify your device. This token is only
            valid within our app used to identify your device and is not linked
            to any personal information. We use the token for push notifications
            and support requests.
2. Use of Your Information
We may use your information for the following purposes:
Account Management:
To create and manage your
            account.
Communication:
To send you updates, newsletters,
            and other information related to CozyBrushery.
Customer Support:
To respond to your inquiries and
            provide support.
3. Disclosure of Your Information
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information
          to third parties except as described in this Privacy Policy:
Service Providers:
We may share information with
            third-party service providers that assist us in operating our app
            and conducting our business.
Legal Obligations:
We may disclose information if
            required by law or in response to valid requests by public
            authorities.
4. Data Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information
          from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of
          transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100%
          secure.
5. Data Retention
We retain your information for as long as necessary to fulfill the
          purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy unless a longer retention
          period is required or permitted by law.
6. Your Rights
Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:
Access and obtain a copy of your information.
Request correction of any inaccuracies in your information.
Request deletion of your information.
To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information
          provided below.
7. Children's Privacy
CozyBrushery is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do
          not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If
          you become aware that a child has provided us with personal
          information, please contact us.
8. Third-Party Services
Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are
          not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties. We
          encourage you to review their privacy policies.
9. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify
          you of any changes by updating the "Effective Date" at the top of this
          policy. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for
          any changes.
10. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy,
          please contact us at:
Netogami Co. Ltd.
Address: JP-BASE Shibuya Shoto 101, 1-28-14, Shoto, Shibuya-ku,
            Tokyo 1500046
By using CozyBrushery, you consent to the collection and use of your
          information as described in this Privacy Policy.